(A) Dorsal habitus; male. (B) Head and pronotum; arrow shows circular punctuation; male. (C) Part of thorax; arrow shows circular punctuation on mesoacetabulum; ventrolateral view; male. (D) Fore leg; arrow shows tibial grasping comb; lateral view; male. (E) Proctiger; lateral view; male. (F) Paramere; lateral view; male. (G) Paramere; laterocaudal view; male. (H) Dorsal habitus; female. Scale bar 1.00 mm.
</paragraph>
